{"tid":350416,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"「媽媽說18歲才可以...」　男哄少女：媽媽不會知道","createTime":"2017-08-07T08:28:05.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-07T08:37:18.000Z","uid":122,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"7cd1b794cafdea7f03592436ce35a36ca0160365","tid":350416,"uid":122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-07T08:28:05.000Z","msg":"桃園一名蕭姓男子（26歲）遭控性侵未滿16歲少女，然少女面對檢察官調查時指稱，兩人交往一段時間後，在去年8月底和去年11月間發生2次性關係，其中第一次是她自願的，而第二次她有跟蕭男說：「媽媽說18歲以後才能做愛」，可是蕭男對她說「沒關係，媽媽不會知道的」，少女於是就跟蕭男發生性關係了。<br />\n<br />\n由於少女是2000年6月出生，其所指証與蕭男發生性行為的時間，是在她滿16歲之後，並未觸犯刑法227條為保護少年而訂「與16歲以下少年發生性行為、不論是自願或強迫均屬有罪」之規定，且少女又坦承未抗拒與蕭男發生性關係等情，桃園地檢署<span style=\"color: red;\">今予以不起訴處分</span>。（突發中心張沛森／桃園報導）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.whoateallthepies.tv/wp-content/uploads/2014/01/ronaldo-bale.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.whoateallthepies.tv%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2014%2F01%2Fronaldo-bale.gif&h=e4ec4d25&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"bd509a4c6ea8965cbcbc63335a094015bf975d07","tid":350416,"uid":49055,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-07T08:31:13.000Z","msg":"還我處女"},{"pid":"18e2eda2e312f606608b91be36c9d730eea738aa","tid":350416,"uid":1139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-07T08:33:10.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d695a3587fbe80b3b0c053d148a1fcdfcddcf071","tid":350416,"uid":118623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-07T08:33:18.000Z","msg":"今場桃園爆冷跑出"},{"pid":"ce10cd20547196c105784610029541cd872c62b4","tid":350416,"uid":41508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-07T08:34:35.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f4bd255253c8f933f8ea91156aef86f93252cea0","tid":350416,"uid":17081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-07T08:37:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}